PrecisAuthority for the Secretary of State for External Affairs (a) to sign (i) an AGREEMENT on a COMPREHENSIVE POLITICAL SETTLEMENT of the CAMBODIA CONFLICT, and (ii) an Agreement concerning the Sovereignty, Independence, Territorial Integrity and Inviolability, Neutrality and National Unity of Cambodia, OR (b) to execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing Ambassador Alan Sullivan to sign those Agreements.

precis:
Authority for the Secretary of State for External Affairs (a) to sign (i)
an AGREEMENT on a COMPREHENSIVE POLITICAL SETTLEMENT of the CAMBODIA
CONFLICT, and (ii) an Agreement concerning the Sovereignty, Independence,
Territorial Integrity and Inviolability, Neutrality and National Unity of
Cambodia, OR (b) to execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers
authorizing Ambassador Alan Sullivan to sign those Agreements.
